PRODUCT DESCRIPTION (Max 200 characters: Looking for a credit card where you'll earn Qantas Points every time you spend? You've found it. The Bankwest Qantas MasterCard offers you exactly this, helping you to get to your dream destination sooner.
REWARDS DESCRIPTION (bullet points):
-20,000 bonus Qantas Points*
'-Earn 1 Qantas Point^ for every $2 you spend on eligible purchases
'- If you're eligible for Platinum, enjoy 0.50 Qantas points for every $1 you spend on eligible purchase#
REWARDS TERMS AND CONDITIONS:
-Rewards Program
'--*This offer is available for a limited time and only to new Bankwest Qantas MasterCard customers who apply for a Bankwest Qantas MasterCard between 3 March 2015 and 31 May 2015 and meet minimum spend requirements. bonus points are subject to change. You will only be able to earn bonus Qantas Points when you have spent at least $2,500 on eligible purchases within 3 months from account opening. Bonus Qantas Points will only be transferred to your account within the month after the end of the 3 month period from account opening. Bonus points will contribute to annual points cap. #Qantas Points are earned on eligible purchases only. Exclusions, limitations and Qantas Points caps apply. The total Qantas Points (including Bonus Points) that can be earned in Each Year are 50,000 Qantas Points for Bankwest Qantas Classic Mastercard, 66,667 Qantas Points for Bankwest Qantas Gold Mastercard and 200,000 Qantas Points for Bankwest Qantas Platinum Mastercard. Qantas Points, outside any bonus Qantas Points, will only be transferred to your Qantas Frequent Flyer account at the end of the 2 month period from account opening and once you have spent at least $1,500 on eligible purchases. Fees and charges apply, T&Cs apply and available on request.
'-Frequent Flyer Membership
'--^You must be a member of the Qantas Frequent Flyer program to earn and redeem Qantas Points.  If you aren't already a Qantas Frequent Flyer member, Bankwest has organised for the membership joining fee to be waived for new cardholders who join at qantas.com/joinffbankwest. Membership and the earning and redemption of Qantas Points are subject to the Qantas Frequent Flyer program terms and conditions available at qantas.com/terms.
MINIMUM MONTHLY REPAYMENT: Greater of 2% of the closing balance or $20, whichever is greater
